snippet.title: Panic In The Woods | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Panic in the Woods is a horror survival and extraction game playable in single player or co-op for up to 4 players. Lost in a creepy forest, you and your friends are hunted by a monster. Stay quiet while extracting keys through nightmarish realms, using items like traps, sonars, and flare guns to survive!

Get ready to run and hide this September, on Friday the 13th!

WHISHLIST NOW! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3036880/Panic_In_The_Woods/
